    "intro": "Today's nightly tightens the seams across remote chat and the desktop updater: stalled harness sessions now fail loudly instead of hanging on \"connecting\", Windows updates leave a paper trail and reliably relaunch, and a cluster of interface fixes keeps streamed agent replies, sidebar previews, and the chat composer from flickering or losing focus.",
