        "title": "Remote chat sessions keep their org identity",
        "summary": "Server-side fix so harness-backed chat sessions always carry the org context the remote runtime needs.",
        "items": [
          {
            "text": "Chat sessions now backfill the X-Aura-Org-Id header from the project when agent metadata is missing it, so remote harness sessions no longer drop org context mid-handshake.",
