            "confidence": "high"
          },
          {
            "text": "Agent chats now preserve the streamed assistant tail until persisted history semantically catches up, so finished replies stop blinking or briefly reverting to stale content.",
            "commit_shas": [
              "db539c0242b7d3e009c42ca3ad4619d6fab3c5f4"
            ],
            "confidence": "high"
          },
          {
            "text": "The swarm harness now wakes hibernating agents on demand instead of leaving them idle when a turn arrives.",
